WEBVTT

00:01.634 --> 00:04.085
Cheers is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:04.120 --> 00:05.553
(bell ringing)

00:05.588 --> 00:07.655
Oh, here you go,
pal. Let me, uh...

00:07.689 --> 00:08.823
(laughs) Sorry.

00:08.857 --> 00:10.658
I don't have any change on me.

00:10.659 --> 00:12.527
That's all right.
God bless you anyway.

00:12.528 --> 00:13.728
FRASIER:
Hey, Sam.

00:13.762 --> 00:15.530
Hey, Frasier, how
you doing, man?

00:15.531 --> 00:17.215
I tell you, I used to
have change all the time,

00:17.216 --> 00:18.383
but things are tough now.

00:18.384 --> 00:20.786
The bar burned down, you know.

00:20.887 --> 00:22.337
This is the place right here.

00:22.371 --> 00:23.638
Yeah, burned down,

00:23.673 --> 00:25.740
and I've been spending
every dime I have

00:25.775 --> 00:27.575
just to rebuild the place.

00:27.576 --> 00:29.911
I don't have anyone to
blame but myself really.

00:29.912 --> 00:31.145
And women. Oh, God.

00:31.180 --> 00:32.313
(laughs)

00:32.348 --> 00:33.715
Me and women.

00:33.716 --> 00:35.100
Oh. Yeah, I tell
you, I think...

00:35.101 --> 00:37.369
I think it first started for me

00:37.370 --> 00:40.138
when I hired this really bright,
blonde waitress, you know.

00:40.139 --> 00:41.606
Her name was Diane.

00:41.607 --> 00:42.857
Maybe you heard about her.

00:42.858 --> 00:44.325
Used to come in and out
of here all the time.

00:44.326 --> 00:46.427
Five years ago,
books under her arm...

00:46.756 --> 00:50.931
And then Rebecca, you
know, finally admitted,

00:50.932 --> 00:52.800
"Yeah, I burned
the bar down."

00:52.835 --> 00:54.352
I forgave her.

00:54.386 --> 00:55.670
Good night, Sam.

00:55.705 --> 00:57.289
Yeah, good night, Fras!

00:57.290 --> 00:58.472
And then, listen to this.

00:58.473 --> 00:59.640
Rebecca finally

00:59.641 --> 01:01.609
admits to me, "Yes, I
burned the bar down."

01:01.610 --> 01:03.111
(whoops) Was I mad, I tell you.

01:03.112 --> 01:04.412
But what are you gonna do?

01:04.413 --> 01:06.547
Are you gonna stick her
with guilt the rest of...

01:06.548 --> 01:08.116
Sam?
Yeah?

01:08.150 --> 01:09.283
There you go.

01:09.318 --> 01:10.451
Thank you.

01:10.485 --> 01:12.854
Come this way. Oh.

01:12.888 --> 01:14.189
Here you go.

01:14.223 --> 01:16.123
You earned it.

01:18.493 --> 01:20.178
(theme song begins)

01:22.248 --> 01:24.582
♪ Sometimes you want to go ♪

01:24.616 --> 01:28.386
♪ Where everybody
knows your name ♪

01:30.356 --> 01:34.592
♪ And they're always
glad you came ♪

01:34.626 --> 01:37.262
♪ You wanna be
where you can see ♪

01:37.296 --> 01:39.831
♪ Our troubles
are all the same ♪

01:39.865 --> 01:44.635
♪ You wanna go where
everybody knows your name. ♪

